---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="About — Barker & Bow" description="The story behind our handmade dog scarves.">
  <section class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-5 pt-14 pb-10 grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-10 items-center">
    <div>
      <span class="inline-block rounded-full bg-blush px-4 py-1.5 text-sm font-semibold text-terracotta-dark">
        Our story
      </span>
      <h1 class="mt-5 font-display text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-semibold leading-tight">
        Made by hand, with a dog at our feet
      </h1>
      <p class="mt-5 text-ink-soft leading-relaxed">
        <!-- TODO: Replace with your real story -->
        Barker &amp; Bow started with one scrappy rescue pup and a box of fabric
        offcuts too pretty to throw away. What began as a single scarf for our own
        dog turned into a little workshop full of colour, pattern and wagging tails.
      </p>
      <p class="mt-4 text-ink-soft leading-relaxed">
        Today every scarf is still cut, sewn and finished by hand in small batches.
        We choose soft, hard-wearing fabrics, double-stitch the seams, and check
        each one ourselves before it heads out to its new home.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="aspect-[4/5] overflow-hidden rounded-[2rem] bg-cream-deep shadow-lg">
      <img src="https://placedog.net/720/900?id=20" alt="The maker with a dog" class="h-full w-full object-cover" />
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-5 py-12">
    <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
      <div class="rounded-2xl bg-white p-6 ring-1 ring-cream-deep">
        <h3 class="font-display text-xl font-semibold">Thoughtfully sourced</h3>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-ink-soft leading-relaxed">We pick fabrics for softness and durability — comfy on the neck, tough enough for adventures.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="rounded-2xl bg-white p-6 ring-1 ring-cream-deep">
        <h3 class="font-display text-xl font-semibold">Made in small batches</h3>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-ink-soft leading-relaxed">No factories, no rush. Each piece gets our full attention from cut to final stitch.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="rounded-2xl bg-white p-6 ring-1 ring-cream-deep">
        <h3 class="font-display text-xl font-semibold">Five sizes</h3>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-ink-soft leading-relaxed">From tiny pups to humans — including matching scarves for you. Not sure which size? We'll help you measure.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-5 pb-4">
    <div class="rounded-3xl bg-sage/15 px-8 py-12 text-center">
      <h2 class="font-display text-3xl font-semibold">Say hello</h2>
      <p class="mt-3 text-ink-soft max-w-md mx-auto">We love hearing from fellow dog people. Questions, custom ideas, or just photos of your pup — all welcome.</p>
      <a href="/contact" class="mt-6 inline-flex items-center rounded-full bg-terracotta px-6 py-3 font-semibold text-cream hover:bg-terracotta-dark transition-colors">
        Contact us
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
